

# Superstore Sales & Profitability Dashboard (Power BI)

*Business-focused Power BI dashboard analyzing sales and profitability using Superstore data.*

Interactive Power BI report built to provide an executive sales overview and a profitability deep dive for Furniture.

## Pages
### 1) Executive Sales Overview
- KPIs: Total Sales, Total Profit, Profit Margin, Orders, Average Order Value
- Dynamic title by year
- Sales trend with reference line (average)
- Sales by Category
- YoY indicator for Total Sales

### 2) Profitability Analysis – Furniture
- Profit Margin by Subcategory (identifies loss drivers)
- Profit vs Discount relationship by Subcategory (quadrant analysis)
- Year filter (single select) to make YoY comparisons consistent
- KPI: Furniture Profit Margin with YoY change in percentage points (pp)

## Key Insight
Furniture shows a negative profit margin mainly driven by **Tables**, where high discounts are strongly associated with losses.

## Recommendation
Review discount strategy for **Tables** and assess shipping cost impact.

## Tools / Skills
Power BI • DAX (Time Intelligence) • Data Modeling • Dashboard UX • Storytelling

